text: Keki Adhikari (; born February 2, 1989) is a Nepalese actress and a professional model. She is one of the successful Nepali actress. She has played dozens of Nepali Movies, Music Videos & Television Ads. She debut in Nepali Film Industry from her first movie called "Swor". She was widely recognized from superhit Nepali movie Shree 5 Ambare. She had won various National Film Awards.
